ression of its asymptotic variance, together with\nconsistent variance estimators. The resulting inferential tools can be used\nwhen both $K$ and $p$ are independent of the sample size $n$, and when both, or\neither, $p$ and $K$ vary with $n$, while allowing for $p > n$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 May 2019 19:37:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Apr 2020 03:13:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 2 Mar 2021 22:44:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-04"}
