ivariate risk\nmeasures. Finally, we show that our multivariate expectiles indeed allow\nperforming multiple-output expectile regression, which is illustrated on\nsimulated and real data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 May 2019 20:50:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-31"}
