ar half-life, we evaluated the activity levels from the exposure\ntimes and determined a cosmogenic activation rate that is consistent with other\nmeasurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 May 2019 05:51:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Sep 2019 02:26:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-09"}
