ency\nstatements are unconditional and improve on earlier theorems of [KO17] and\n[BM18] on the consistency of lower bounds with $\\mathsf{PV}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 May 2019 09:51:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Dec 2019 09:35:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 24 Feb 2020 13:26:45 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 16 Jun 2020 18:41:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-25"}
